div><div class="t m7f1 x71 h27 y1141 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God showed him ? </div><div class="t m1d2 x64 h27 y209b ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m8c x66 h27 y138c ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What, then, did the animals that Peter saw in </div><div class="t m31f x71 h27 y135d ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vision represent? </div><div class="t m1d5 x64 h27 y1ce4 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m5f5 x66 h27 y1db5 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why did he so readily come to the call of Corne-</div><div class="t m218 x71 h27 y133d ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lius? What question did he ask? </div><div class="t m127 x29 h27 y110c ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t m671 x63 h27 y15d4 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Relate the reply of Cornelius. </div><div class="t m2cc x74 h27 yf48 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Io. For what did he say they were all waiting? In </div><div class="t m468 x71 h27 y1340 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whose presence did they feel themselves to be? </div><div class="t m476 x29 h27 y1341 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. What did Peter say that he perceived by all this? </div><div class="t me4 x74 h27 y1193 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. </div><div class="t md30 x5b h27 y12ad ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How many are accepted with God? </div><div class="t me4 x74 h27 yf50 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t m115f x63 h27 y12ae ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What word did those present know? </div><div class="t me4 x74 h27 y105f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">14. </div><div class="t mbbc x5b h27 y12af ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To whom was the word sent? What did the </div><div class="t m381 x26 h27 y1060 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">word preach? </div><div class="t me4 x74 h27 y1392 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">15. </div><div class="t m386 x5b h27 y1d77 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Where was it.made known? </div><div class="t m283 x49 h13 y1127 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">IN COUNTRIES AROUND MEDITERRANEAN SEA </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.00